Femi Fani-Kayode has once again taken to twitter to blast Nigeria’s richest industrialist, Aliko Dangote. In a tweet on Thursday, He wrote, ”Why do Dangote trucks kill more people in a month in Nigeria than Covid 19 and malaria and how come they get away with it? Why are they smuggling thousands of almajiris, ISWA and Boko Haram fighters and Fulani herdsmen into the south every day? What is Aliko Dangote up to?” Why do Dangote trucks kill more people in a month in Nigeria than Covid 19 and malaria and how come they get away with it? Why are they smuggling thousands of almajiris, ISWA and Boko Haram fighters and Fulani herdsmen into the south every day? What is Aliko Dangote up to?